/*
 * Gameplay:
 * - 2 players alternate turns
 * - Each turn: Roll dice up to 3 times
 * - Hold dice between rolls with buttons 1-5
 * - After rolls, select scoring category
 * - Game ends after 26 turns (13 categories × 2 players)
 */

